Hw3: Projections

Jason Lubrano
CSCI4229/5229 Fall 2018

Draw a mech army
Draw several mechs on the screen
Demonstrate rotation, size, and scaling

Key bindings
	1			Draws small camo mech
	2			Draws medium mech
	3			Draws biggest mech
	4			Draws mech army (default)
	9			Toggles whether we rotate or not
	m/M 		Toggle between perspective and orthogonal
	+/- 		Changes field of view for perspective
	a/A 		Toggle axes
	arrows 		Change view angle
	PgDn/PgUp	Zoom in and out
	0 			Reset view angle
	ESC			Exit


Time Taken: 8 hours